title: Cinnabar Acupuncture Grand Opening Fort Myers FL
text:
(MENAFN Press) Cinnabar Acupuncture Grand Opening Fort Myers FL Cinnabar Acupuncture has moved from 4S Ranch Commons 10432 Reserve Dr Ste 111 to historic downtown Fort Myers FL. 
Scientific Calculator Online PR News – 15-September-2015 – Cinnabar acupuncture is a Chinese medicine clinic offering acupuncture cosmetic acupuncture natural skincare endermologie and slimming detox treatments. Mother/daughter doctors of acupuncture and Chinese medicine Drs. Judith and Lia Andrews DAOM L.Ac. have moved their acupuncture clinic from the 4S Ranch community in San Diego CA to historic downtown Fort Myers FL. Cinnabar Acupuncture was the premiere clinic and spa for acupuncture massage natural skincare and endermologie as is reflected in their Yelp reviews: http://www.yelp.com/biz/cinnabar-acupuncture-clinic-and-spa-san-diego-3. 
Cinnabar Acupuncture Fort Myers brings the same dedication to offering professional patient care in a clean relaxing environment. Cinnabars acupuncture doctors mentored with Chinese medical doctors in California and China and have over 10 years of experience in Family Medicine including skin issues menstrual and menopausal symptoms sports injuries digestive disturbances pain management postpartum recovery fertility childhood eczema and more. Cinnabar also specializes in cosmetic treatments including acupuncture facelift endermologie and slimming detox treatments. 
Cinnabar acupuncturists are adept at treating all ages from infants to seniors offering an array of modalities including gentle acupuncture cupping moxibustion gua sha qigong exercises ear acupressure magnet therapy and warm stone massage. An extensive Chinese herbal pharmacy includes glycerin-based tinctures pills powder extracts and raw herbs for internal and topical use. 
Cinnabar accommodates every schedule offering weekend and evening appointments. Treatments are available by appointment only. View our treatments on Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/user/CinnabarAcupuncture. 
Please visit http://cinnabaracupuncture.com or call 305.590.8474 for more information.
